description.narrative: In 2019, UNICEF focused on expanding partnerships to reinforce its positioning on global and national priorities. Building on its leading presence on digital media, EC produced more than 11 campaigns covering key aspects of its programmatic engagement, for a total reach of 150 million and an engagement rate of 7%. In addition, EC reinforced its presence in media, receiving nearly 500 mentions. With major events like the CRC@30, where the Pyramids were lit in Blue, and the development of partnerships with high-profile organizations like Al-Ahly and the Gouna Film Festival, EC strategically reinforced UNICEF's positioning as the Voice for Children. | Status:On-track | As-of Date:12/12/2019
